
<h1 class="govuk-heading-l datagovuk-heading-l">Property price paid</h1>

<section class="govuk-section datagovuk-section">
  <p class="govuk-body-m datagovuk-body">Property price paid data is a comprehensive record of residential property transactions in England and Wales, as recorded by HM Land Registry. The data includes the sale price, date of transfer, property type (detached, semi-detached, terraced, flat/maisonette, or other), tenure (freehold or leasehold), and whether the property is a new build. Find properties by searching by any combination of these characteristics. </p>
<p class="govuk-body-m datagovuk-body">You can use this data to understand market activity, conduct research and inform decisions about buying and selling property.</p>
</section>


